title: Grace Brown Rides Momentum into La Vuelta Femenina after ‘Biggest Win of Career’
content:
Taking Liège-Bastogne-Liège on Sunday marks highpoint of Australian’s career: 'Sometimes patience works. I’m happy that it paid off.'

Read the full article at Grace Brown Rides Momentum into La Vuelta Femenina after ‘Biggest Win of Career’ on Velo.
